name: Oli6 Goat Milk Follow On Formula (6 to 12 months) Halal Certified
description:
Oli6® Dairy Goat Follow-On Formula is a premium dairy goat milk-based formula that is nutritionally tailored with a balance of key ingredients for formula fed babies aged 6 to 12 months. Our Follow-On Formula balances the natural benefits of goat milk with scientific smarts in development and formulation to make sure your baby’s needs are met every step of the way.

Oli6® Follow-On Formula is proudly manufactured in Victoria, Australia and we ensure that all ingredients used meet strict Australian regulations and requirements.  

This baby formula is:

Made from Dairy Goat Milk
Goats milk is a natural source of Magnesium for normal growth and development, Vitamin A for eye and vision development, calcium for strong bones and teeth, and Vitamin C for immunity
Has naturally occurring prebiotic Oligos to help provide gut and immune health
Naturally gentle on tiny tummies
Nutritionally complete
Provides the benefits 18 essential vitamins and minerals to support normal growth and development in children*
Contains Calcium and Vitamin D for normal bone and teeth structure*
Enriched with iron and zinc which are necessary for normal immune system function*
Manufactured in Australia, adhering to the strict Australian regulatory guideline
Oli6® Follow-On Formula Goat milk is the smart choice because it contains around six times the oligos* of cows' milk. Oligos* have been suggested to provide gut & immune health and help to promote beneficial bacteria in humans. The Oli6® goat milk follow-on formula is a popular choice among parents who want to supplement their child’s diet. For parents whose children may be fussy eaters, Oli6® goat milk follow-on formula may provide the child with additional nutrients that help with their development.

What are the main ingredients of Oli6 goat milk follow-on formula?
Main Ingredients: Lactose, goat milk solids (full cream milk powder, whey protein powder), vegetable oils (including soybean), DHA powder, ARA powder, minerals (calcium carbonate, sodium citrate, ferric pyrophosphate, sodium selenite, zinc oxide, copper gluconate, manganese sulphate, potassium iodide), oligosaccharides (2'-O-fucosyllactose, lacto-N-neotetraose), choline bitartrate, vitamins (C, E, A, D3, B5, B3, K1, B2, B1, B12, B6, B9, B7), L-methionine, Bifidobacterium longum (BB536), taurine, inositol, L-carnitine, lutein.

Allergen declaration: This follow-on formula contains goat milk and soybean products.
The protein source of Oli6® Follow-On Formula is derived from goat milk casein and whey protein.

name: Graco Pack n Play Playard
description: This is a 19 year-old Graco Pack n Play Playard [playpen]. However it is clean and in very good condition. The playpen is good to use from birth up to 13.5kg, both for sleeping and keeping the baby safe when she/he is awake and playing with their toys.  The changing table that comes with it is good to use from birth up to 10kg. It has got 2 wheels on one side, which makes the playpen easy to bring from one room to another if you need to keep an eye on your baby whilst doing chores at home. The wheels can be locked so that the playpen will safely stay in one place. The playpen is also easy to pack up and store in a corner if space is needed in the home. This playpen has sentimental value to me, but I would like to pass it on in the hope that it can be used again.
